                              'Noblik' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  @{" Noblik " link play} is a Workbench game where the goal is to move diagonal
bars on a 7 by 7 tile board, and the more you move, the more points
you get. To complicate matters a little, avoid moving bars so their
ends 'touch' the ends of bars that are located nearby... if that
happens, those bars will explode and the game will be over.

  Have fun!

